title: Spanish official brushes off Trump’s NATO expulsion remarks: ‘We are not worried’

author: Addy Bink
description: These states have all affirmed that they want to observe daylight saving time year-round, yet their clocks will switch to standard time in November with the rest of us. Here's why.
title: These states approved permanent daylight saving time: Why their clocks still change in November
